        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2333191902" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer8339745507620803852">One of my favorite movies of all time. A letdown of a book. Good thing Lorenzo Semple Jr. got hold of the screenplay and made it into the movie he did. The strange sexual politics, which works with Redford and Dunaway, does not work here. But one thing I like: the book is set in Georgetown and Alexandria instead of New York. That’s pretty neat.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


